                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "神变 · 恶曜开眼"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>，其他我方角色获得2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">充能</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/8d02cb476ba0314a99ce5e7ecc3b4904_5324620187041151837.png",
                "id": "talent59020",
                "key": "奥义 · 梦想真说",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "奥义 · 梦想真说"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，初始附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">诸愿百眼之轮</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/f18816cd4d10b81b8610917baa51d71a_6406089043228945462.png",
                "id": "talent54974",
                "key": "诸愿百眼之轮",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "诸愿百眼之轮"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此召唤物在场时：</span>我方角色「元素爆发」造成的伤害+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_867745249623681086.png",
                "id": "talent98638",
                "key": "雷罚恶曜之眼",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/22/88072335/75f1d2ef52221da67ee1c52ce97af966_6434300959168258799.png",
                "title": "雷罚恶曜之眼"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/27/88072335/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_907607797141741861.png",
                "id": "talent24346",
                "key": "雷元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">充能</span></strong></p><p>角色使用「元素爆发」时，需要消耗充能。</p><p>角色使用「元素战技」或「普通攻击」后，会获得1点充能。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">诸愿百眼之轮</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">其他我方角色使用「元素爆发」后：</span>累积1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「愿力」</span>。（最多累积3点）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色使用</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">奥义 · 梦想真说</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">时：</span>消耗所有<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「愿力」</span>，每点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">「愿力」</span>使造成的伤害+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/30/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_6957952504540033349.png",
